{
  "stem": "19596.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The glasses were sorted, the eye-- the thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, you know-- and they came to supervise it and was counted and registered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, the Germans are very efficient with registering and counting and things like that, very efficient, like computers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got the news about Stalingrad from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They talked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the Germans talked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not the Germans talked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those idiots they hired them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were Ukrainians who used to be in the Russian army and the Soviet army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they-- there-- there was a general called Vlasov.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took all the men out of the prisoner camps, all the Ukrainians and things like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he formed a SS battalion, which was authorized by the German government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were guards in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Croatians were guards in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Estonians were guards in the camp, and the Lithuanians and Latvians were guards in the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we all knew about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was a underground in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a underground.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I can only tell you what I know, because each cell didn't know from another cell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was organized in such a way that if they torture somebody, he only can give away two people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was affiliated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the people-- to the people who were in there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's to gather information, pass them on very slowly to the Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very carefully [? to whom. ?]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, just-- just carrying information.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing active.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing with ammunition.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing with escaping.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was not in escape committee.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The escape committee was organized by Poles, by sophisticated Poles.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now you see, in-- even if a Jew escapes from Auschwitz, he would not get far, because of the anti-Semitic atmosphere outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
